UPDATE public.questions SET
  stimulus_text = 'The popularity of television programs featuring home renovations has exploded in recent years, as viewers eagerly seek inspiration for their own home improvement projects. But, some critics argue that these shows promote a narrow, idealized version of home design. They point out that the majority of these programs focus on lavish, contemporary remodels and renovations, which are often not feasible for most homeowners. In addition, critics argue that these shows often fail to address issues of sustainability and accessibility, which can be important considerations for home improvement projects. Many of these shows also fail to highlight the diverse range of design styles and approaches that exist beyond the sleek, modern aesthetic. What is the most likely reason why the author chooses to include the sentence "In addition, critics argue that these shows often fail to address issues of sustainability and accessibility, which can be important considerations for home improvement projects."?',
  question_text = 'The author likely includes the sentence "In addition, critics argue that these shows often fail to address issues of sustainability and accessibility, which can be important considerations for home improvement projects." to',
